text:
Hotel ini memang layak disebut hotel butik karena konsepnya cukup unik yaitu menggabungkan beberapa kontainer untuk  menjadi bangunan hotel. 

Yang mungkin bisa Anda pertimbangan adalah parkirannya lumayan luas di belakang sehingga tidak perlu khawatir susah parkir, selain itu servisnya ramah bahkan kamar kami di-upgrade menjadi deluxe.

Kamar deluxe mempunyai ukuran yang luas, terdapat bench dan meja panjang. Kamar mandi agak sempit dan berpartisi kaca tanpa kunci dan kalo melongo dari luar maka agak kelihatan aktivitas di dalam, cocok untuk bulan madu. Tips menginap di sini : minta pemandangan menghadap ke jalan, karena sebagian besar hotel ini menghadap ke lobi dan akan terlihat dari lobi.

Fasilitas sarapan disediakan dari Portable, selain itu lobby nya mempunyai banyak kursi sehingga bisa digunakan untuk bekerja dan bertemu dengan orang. Air minum tersedia di dispenser

MInusnya hanya kurang kedap saja kalau ada yang lompat² di atas.

Waktu itu juga disediakan sepeda untuk dipakai secara cuma² dengan deposit. 
Intinya cukup puas di sini

title: Well located, Comfortable, Excellent Service!

text:
This hotel is recommended for those who are in need of a weekend gateway. The room are spacious plus the location is perfect. We were surrounded by shopping centre and delicious food places. Unfortunately the food service in-house were so disappointing. The breakfast buffet was totally disaster. Food options such as eggs, milk, bread/cereals, coffee and tea are basic necessities for hotel breakfast. However you can’t find the basics at Qubika. Coffee powder being served in a bowl where everyone can touch the same spoon? C’mon! Don’t you have covid protocol? 
I think instant coffee (sachet) would be more appropriate and hygienic. Not to mention the eating utensils still has food stain on it although it’s wrapped in plastic. This is totally unacceptable! Bad service and cleanliness at portable (the restaurant). 
Overall, besides the breakfast situation it was enjoyable experience staying at Qubika BSD.
Every corner of the hotel are instagramable!
title: Stylish Staycation And Breakfast for Looser!

title: Stop over

text:
Found this hotel with unique look and design while on business trip at Gading Serpong area.

Hotel's interior very instagramble look, with stack of containers (yes, containers) as rooms (although i dont know if these are real containers or only look like containers).

I got deluxe room, clean, good ac, good bed, and have enough space for this price range. Bathroom clean, standard size for this price range.
TV channel with cable tv, but picture quality not sharp and good.

Hotel didnt provide bottled water, but they provided glass water jug and you can take water at dispenser location. No teabag or coffee sachet provided. Bathroom amenities provided.

There are rooms with window inside view of the hotel (fronting other room, less privacy if you open the curtain) and rooms with window outside view.

Breakfast is ok.
Plenty of parking space for your car.

Overall is ok, and will be on my list if i need to stay in that area again.
title: New Hotel. Fit For Business Traveller.
